# Ansible Cheatsheet

### To see list of connection types with managed Node
#### ansible-doc -t connection -l
#### or
#### ansible-doc --type connection --list

### ansible copy module
#### ansible -m copy -a "src=path_along_with_file dest=/Destination_path" localhost/any_remote_server

### check flag, it is used to check if there is any changes made in dest file
#### ansible -m copy -a "src=usman.txt dest=/home/usmannow3/Ansible-Test" --check localhost

### diff flag, it is used to show exact changes made while performing specific task/change
#### ansible -m copy -a "src=usman.txt dest=/home/usmannow3/Ansible-Test" --diff localhost

